      '## 3. swagger-expert (Blue)',
      'Genera documentacion OpenAPI 3.0 completa analizando el codigo Spring Boot.',
      '```yaml\nname: swagger-expert\nmodel: claude-sonnet-4-5\ncolor: blue\nallowed_tools: [Read, Write, Grep, Glob, Bash]\n```',
